@Karolina F "What I truly find ignorant is judging people's intelligence based solely on their use of one discourse marker."<br/>
You miss the point.  People DO judge others for shallow reasons or other first impressions.  Human nature.  Can't get away from it.  Gotta deal with it by putting your best verbal foot forward.<br/>
Sadly, many a young female feels lucky if a male counterpart even makes it up to her neck when they first meet, let alone uses his ears.
